ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would describe the course as exciting and meaningfully informative.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: The course, readings, discussion, and out of class conversations continue to influence the work I am producing in my work as an MFA candidate in painting and printmaking. I believe that Professor Mercer's work in very important to the way we as artists understand art history. I recommend his courses to all of my fellow students in the School of Art.
